(Republished)

Mohamed Shawkat, Petitioner, v. Helmsley-Spear, Inc., et al., Respondents.

Determination of the State Human Rights Appeal Board, dated November 30, 1973, unanimously confirmed, without costs and without disbursements, and the petition dismissed. The order of this court entered on February 19,1974, is vacated. No opinion. Concur — Markewich, J. P., Nunez, Kupferman, Steuer and Lane, JJ. [43 A D 2d 1016.]
